Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.13,0:00:04.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在学园祭即将到来之时
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.44,0:00:11.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到竟会有这样的危机造访轻音部
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.46,0:00:16.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心情不错嘛  梓
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.93,0:00:17.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.32,0:00:22.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一想到马上就能在学园祭上演出
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.16,0:00:22.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心里就很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.26,0:00:24.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新兵上阵呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.41,0:00:27.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去年轻音部的演出我也好想看呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.68,0:00:33.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澪去年可是很活跃呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.79,0:00:34.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.95,0:00:36.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在舞台上摔倒…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.22,0:00:37.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇～！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.71,0:00:40.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是把去年学园祭的演出都拍下来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.16,0:00:43.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想看我想看！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.10,0:00:46.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓啊  你不再考虑下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.37,0:00:47.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小唯  小律
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.51,0:00:51.24,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放～开～我～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.13,0:00:52.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  先从我推荐的经典场景开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.62,0:00:53.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要看啊  梓  
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.85,0:00:55.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很危险的哦  会被诅咒的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.36,0:00:59.09,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,条纹啊条纹～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.43,0:00:59.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看…看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.39,0:01:00.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.52,0:02:38.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.02,0:02:43.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家只有在上场时的演奏才爆种啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.23,0:02:45.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变得会说话了呢～  你这家伙～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.19,0:02:51.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.25,0:02:54.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想起了好多事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.61,0:02:59.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  确实  唯那时候的声音…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.10,0:03:03.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对对  早上爬起来就一副破锣嗓子了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.17,0:03:06.66,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是澪就替你当了主唱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.53,0:03:08.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对梓来说  这将是在轻音部的第一次演出呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.79,0:03:09.76,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  真不错呢  小澪的歌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.29,0:03:11.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我会加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.88,0:03:11.64,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢  真好听
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.73,0:03:13.90,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真帅气呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.94,0:03:14.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰你们的兴致真抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.32,0:03:17.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  和  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.92,0:03:20.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么怎么了  你看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.71,0:03:23.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讲堂使用申请书
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.70,0:03:26.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  学园祭的那份你还没交吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.94,0:03:28.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  忘掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.58,0:03:29.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这么粗心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.89,0:03:32.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀  你看我这么忙～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.62,0:03:34.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去年也发生过这种事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.99,0:03:37.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那是社团申请…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.59,0:03:38.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.31,0:03:41.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那么梓  你来写吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.85,0:03:43.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  我？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.59,0:03:44.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…倒也行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.84,0:03:49.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看看  使用者「轻音部」…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.01,0:03:52.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  名称是？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.47,0:03:53.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用乐队名怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.84,0:03:54.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.71,0:03:59.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  说起来我们乐队叫什么名字来着
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.66,0:04:03.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「Sweets Smile」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.66,0:04:03.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「Chocolate Melody」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.66,0:04:03.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「恩那组」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.29,0:04:04.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四分五裂…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.61,0:04:06.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没决定呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.50,0:04:08.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁这个机会  我们想名字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.67,0:04:11.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「平泽唯和愉快的姐妹们」怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.99,0:04:13.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们算啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.43,0:04:14.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「Pure·Pure」之类的怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.43,0:04:14.76,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（やぶうち優于フラワーコミックス上刊载的少女漫画）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.11,0:04:17.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捏它就算了  认真点想一个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.84,0:04:20.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亏我还有点认真呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.69,0:04:21.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认真的啊？！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.95,0:04:24.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦  人的品味各不相同嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.78,0:04:25.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  我知道了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.03,0:04:28.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我来决定
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.61,0:04:30.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家再好好考虑下吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.98,0:04:31.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一下子团结了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.28,0:04:35.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那文件过会交到学生会办公室吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.60,0:04:38.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉啊  让你久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.49,0:04:39.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.46,0:04:42.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和和  回去的时候  偶尔喝杯茶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.01,0:04:45.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  过会我短信联系你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.25,0:04:50.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之  那么乐队名给大家一个晚上各自思考
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.34,0:04:51.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来练习吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.56,0:04:52.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.62,0:04:55.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学园祭越来越近了  要有点干劲才行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.12,0:04:56.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.19,0:04:58.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  对了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.69,0:05:01.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总感觉最近我的吉他音不太着调…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.82,0:05:02.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.57,0:05:04.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能让我稍微看下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.16,0:05:08.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔…琴弦都生锈了嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.48,0:05:12.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你上次换弦是什么时候的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.34,0:05:15.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？ 弦能换的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.17,0:05:17.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什么？！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.12,0:05:21.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且…琴颈也弯了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.78,0:05:24.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话八度调音也会变得乱七八糟哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.60,0:05:27.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八…八…琴颈？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.96,0:05:28.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静点  梓！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.24,0:05:31.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的唯是完全理解不了这些的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.17,0:05:36.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之  不好好关心它是不行的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.27,0:05:38.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是把好吉他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.64,0:05:40.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有好好关心它啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.19,0:05:43.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如一起睡觉啊  给它穿衣服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.05,0:05:46.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你关心错地方了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.62,0:05:48.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？  那…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.59,0:05:51.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小佐和老师  帮我想点办法～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.46,0:05:55.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是交给店里弄比较好吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.02,0:05:57.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只是嫌麻烦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.12,0:06:02.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  去下乐器店吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.59,0:06:04.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  用不着这么麻烦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.87,0:06:08.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  快到学园祭了  这样子都不能练习了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.20,0:06:10.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.12,0:06:14.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小律也没有在做护理吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.32,0:06:15.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.40,0:06:16.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.84,0:06:20.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要用一副我肯定不会做的口气来提问
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.68,0:06:23.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,区区一个小律
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.50,0:06:25.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.61,0:06:28.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好  到了 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.36,0:06:31.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  我在这里等你们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.06,0:06:33.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.12,0:06:35.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我是个左撇子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.32,0:06:39.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去看右手用乐器也只会是悲剧而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.48,0:06:41.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.23,0:06:43.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过你看  澪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.76,0:06:46.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像在搞左手展会哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.96,0:06:47.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.60,0:06:53.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这里是天国吗？！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.74,0:06:55.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.36,0:06:59.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店…店员！  这里的我全要了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.57,0:07:00.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  冷静点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.24,0:07:02.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小澪看起来很开心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.22,0:07:05.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为左手的乐器很少呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.48,0:07:08.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们  先走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.60,0:07:09.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.66,0:07:11.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.97,0:07:13.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.54,0:07:16.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要做下吉他的调整
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.45,0:07:18.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  请问是哪位的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.83,0:07:19.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.04,0:07:22.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那么先让我看下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.40,0:07:31.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说…这个…是经典吉他吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.31,0:07:34.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起…就是脏了点…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.13,0:07:36.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才刚买了一年！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.06,0:07:38.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.04,0:07:42.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么…等完工前请在店里稍等片刻
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.38,0:07:43.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.53,0:07:49.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  等完工前我们看点什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.42,0:07:51.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.98,0:07:53.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盯—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.59,0:07:58.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～我的吉他被扒了个精光
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.60,0:07:59.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.67,0:08:04.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  为什么唯前辈会买那把吉他？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.33,0:08:05.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.34,0:08:08.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  不但重  琴颈又粗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.36,0:08:09.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是很难用吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.79,0:08:12.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  因为可爱嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.43,0:08:14.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可爱？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.77,0:08:15.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.47,0:08:20.85,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  可爱吧  难道不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.87,0:08:21.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全搞不明白唯前辈的神经
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.83,0:08:25.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你们久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.54,0:08:26.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.62,0:08:28.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经拜托店员进行护理了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.70,0:08:29.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.09,0:08:31.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  澪前辈呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.17,0:08:33.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  小澪的话她还在…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.05,0:08:35.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.06,0:08:37.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临  大小姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.10,0:08:39.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  你好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.89,0:08:42.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是大小姐吗  好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.12,0:08:44.63,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天有何贵干？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.77,0:08:47.01,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  只是陪朋友来而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.21,0:08:49.53,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那还真是辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.71,0:08:50.56,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.06,0:08:46.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里可是家的乐器连锁店哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.58,0:08:47.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.42,0:08:50.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吓了一跳吧  那种称呼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.01,0:08:52.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让您久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.55,0:08:52.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.06,0:08:53.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.13,0:08:56.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  变得真漂亮啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.13,0:08:59.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从今以后请多做护理…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.37,0:09:01.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉太！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.19,0:09:04.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来还起名字了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.68,0:09:07.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.67,0:09:08.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.28,0:09:11.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…护理费5000日元
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.17,0:09:12.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.99,0:09:16.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要收钱吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.51,0:09:17.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.74,0:09:19.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  那是当然的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.49,0:09:21.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没银子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.64,0:09:22.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.48,0:09:23.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.01,0:09:24.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.72,0:09:30.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  貌似唯前辈不知道做护理是要花钱的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.90,0:09:33.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  是吗  怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.94,0:09:35.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我手头的不知道够不够…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.59,0:09:37.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大…大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.34,0:09:39.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次就当作免费服务啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.19,0:09:41.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  太对不住你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.72,0:09:42.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.70,0:09:44.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为平日受到您父亲的照顾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.10,0:09:46.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.58,0:09:48.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是给你混过去了呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.04,0:09:48.59,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  这里请一定当作免费服务！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.94,0:09:52.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  我们该回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.66,0:09:53.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.08,0:09:54.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…咦？  
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.30,0:09:55.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.16,0:09:57.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  澪前辈她…？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.04,0:10:00.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我去叫她
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.84,0:10:03.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澪  我说回去啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.89,0:10:04.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不干
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.75,0:10:05.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你小学生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.44,0:10:09.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  大家都等你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.24,0:10:09.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不干
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.12,0:10:11.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.57,0:10:13.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  小澪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.29,0:10:15.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…律
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.86,0:10:18.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好～回家家喽～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.20,0:10:19.72,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不干就是不干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.82,0:10:22.38,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  好了  赶快走
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.48,0:10:24.08,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下…危…危险！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.22,0:10:22.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认识的人有把弦重新换上去用的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.50,0:10:23.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.84,0:10:31.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在搞什么嘛  澪～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.38,0:10:32.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.72,0:10:33.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.64,0:10:34.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋律
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.47,0:10:41.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  吉太变干净了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.74,0:10:44.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还给它起名字了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.51,0:10:45.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后我们怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.22,0:10:48.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  这个嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.68,0:10:50.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧！去喝茶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.88,0:10:52.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还喝茶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.46,0:10:53.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.70,0:10:56.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我马上要去和和碰头
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.85,0:10:57.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎～？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.00,0:10:59.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？  和也要来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.82,0:11:00.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去也行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.26,0:11:02.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  对了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.25,0:11:06.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小澪跟和和在同一班级呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.62,0:11:07.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.47,0:11:08.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.38,0:11:10.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我也告诉她一声
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.78,0:11:14.32,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（dj：大家看她这副醋酸脸XD）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.78,0:11:12.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.84,0:11:19.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,K-ON!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.54,0:11:26.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇～  我很早就想来一次这里啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.83,0:11:28.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明没银子…？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.83,0:11:31.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯的单我来买好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.59,0:11:36.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,领到下个月的零用钱  就换我来请你啦～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.33,0:11:37.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那到时候拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.91,0:11:41.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来唯你在轻音部搞得怎么样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.05,0:11:46.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是狗熊掰棒子掰一个丢一个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.52,0:11:47.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是啊是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.98,0:11:50.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管努力一次的话总会出人意料的厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.97,0:11:51.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对对
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.09,0:11:53.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照顾她果然很费神的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.45,0:11:56.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？什么什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.45,0:11:59.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切  那俩家伙气氛不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.05,0:12:02.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可我们又为什么要偷偷藏起来…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.75,0:12:05.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像侦探一样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.29,0:12:09.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  突击！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.68,0:12:10.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.55,0:12:11.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后那个老师就…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.06,0:12:14.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两位小姐～关系不错嘛～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.65,0:12:18.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,律  你来干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.64,0:12:20.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  偶尔路过啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.90,0:12:22.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  小律一个人？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.98,0:12:25.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  她们在那边哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.64,0:12:27.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真的诶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.47,0:12:31.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀～我家的澪平日受您照顾啦～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.10,0:12:32.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…律
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.67,0:12:35.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？什么？有啥不爽的么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.55,0:12:38.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…倒是没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.71,0:12:40.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不就好了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.36,0:12:41.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小律…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.39,0:12:42.07,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么  你在拜托人家什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.58,0:12:44.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰淇淋都化掉了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.76,0:12:50.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇～好漂亮的便当
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.29,0:12:54.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有啦  只是把现成的东西拼了拼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.08,0:12:58.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  你自己做的吗？了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.29,0:13:00.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这样啦  没那么厉害的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.46,0:13:02.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  比起我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.32,0:13:04.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  午餐时间结束～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.92,0:13:06.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  律？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.58,0:13:08.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我这才正要…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.29,0:13:11.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从今天起到学园祭  午休都要用来练习
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.29,0:13:11.58,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（dj：还不能笑…要忍XD）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.98,0:13:12.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.52,0:13:17.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀～不知道今年的学园祭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.54,0:13:20.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澪会再搞些什么大动作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.85,0:13:23.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去年是走光～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.72,0:13:26.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年干脆露脐好啦～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.72,0:13:26.21,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（R：律你已经因爱生恨自我扭曲了XD）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.40,0:13:27.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  还是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.92,0:13:29.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还练不练！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.12,0:13:33.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,练啦～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.57,0:13:35.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.76,0:13:37.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,章鱼烧～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.15,0:13:38.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.81,0:13:41.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马尾～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.98,0:13:42.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.78,0:13:43.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻花辫～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.01,0:13:45.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手…别乱动
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.82,0:13:47.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  你怎么了你！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.16,0:13:52.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  对了对了  我这里还有推荐的超恐怖电影
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.11,0:13:56.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你再这样我就回教室了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.58,0:13:58.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  那你回啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.46,0:14:04.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思啊  碍着你与和愉快的午餐时光了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.46,0:14:04.88,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（dj：不行！这里还不可以笑XXD）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.47,0:14:09.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么时候说过这种话了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.39,0:14:11.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出什么事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.01,0:14:15.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要…要不要喝茶？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.13,0:14:17.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们喝茶吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.46,0:14:20.31,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  今天我正好准备了好吃的点心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.75,0:14:21.51,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.17,0:14:20.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.77,0:14:22.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我该做点什么…做点什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.99,0:14:29.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大…大家  好好在一起练习吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.99,0:14:29.36,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（Rcat：为了轻音部的未来英勇牺牲的梓喵=w=）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.24,0:14:32.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷…冷场了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.72,0:14:37.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  我们练习吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.25,0:14:42.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.39,0:14:44.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.96,0:14:46.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,one two
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.58,0:14:57.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.77,0:15:03.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,律
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.37,0:15:07.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…鼓点没太赶是蛮好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.51,0:15:08.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不是有点软了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.38,0:15:12.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,律？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.33,0:15:16.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  律！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.57,0:15:17.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.73,0:15:20.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道怎么的就没啥状态  
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.18,0:15:23.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放学后再说吧～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.45,0:15:25.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小…小律…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.74,0:15:26.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了  唯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.95,0:15:28.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.81,0:15:32.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋律
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.39,0:15:43.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,律前辈还没来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.90,0:15:47.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天放学也是这样…今天也是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.93,0:15:49.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.94,0:15:54.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看还是小澪你太冷淡了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.22,0:15:55.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.09,0:15:57.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了轻音部的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.49,0:15:59.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就做一天小律的玩物吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.22,0:16:01.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不然…小律她可就…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.80,0:16:05.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会变得心灰意冷…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.34,0:16:07.05,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老板！要最大碗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.10,0:16:09.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,点一碗自己根本吃不完的超大碗牛肉饭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.02,0:16:12.06,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底在做什么啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.91,0:16:15.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而最后就会在重金属的道路上越走越远…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.88,0:16:18.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就再也回不来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.93,0:16:22.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  是失恋时的小佐和老师吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.59,0:16:23.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.90,0:16:28.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…如果她真就这么走掉的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.38,0:16:32.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学园祭的演出  要怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.88,0:16:37.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来练习吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.10,0:16:39.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  可小律她不在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.06,0:16:41.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.46,0:16:42.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.78,0:16:46.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  不去叫律前辈好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.94,0:16:53.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒不如说要找个顶位子的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.50,0:16:54.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.53,0:16:57.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之  虽然说是以防万一啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.52,0:16:59.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.41,0:17:01.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有人可以代替小律！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.92,0:17:03.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.02,0:17:04.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们等她
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.70,0:17:09.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们等她回来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.67,0:17:11.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小律一定会回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.90,0:17:23.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  澪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.75,0:17:24.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真的诶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.16,0:17:26.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  早…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.14,0:17:29.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…小律啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.37,0:17:33.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…我并不是来看她的…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.98,0:17:36.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她请假了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.90,0:17:39.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.17,0:18:15.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澪？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.35,0:18:19.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超能力者吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.28,0:18:23.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.80,0:18:25.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澪走路的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.13,0:18:35.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感冒怎么样了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.79,0:18:38.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…现在还是有点烧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.82,0:18:41.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难怪打鼓没劲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.32,0:18:45.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明马上就到学园祭了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.24,0:18:48.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了  赶快养好病
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.74,0:18:50.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在等你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.47,0:18:52.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家没生我气？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.97,0:18:53.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.44,0:18:55.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澪呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.37,0:18:59.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有  那还用说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.49,0:19:02.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.65,0:19:03.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.95,0:19:05.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有律的鼓…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.10,0:19:07.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总会有些冷清呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.86,0:19:10.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算有点急促
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.14,0:19:12.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也还是喜欢那个充满气势
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.94,0:19:15.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,力道十足的律的鼓点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.52,0:19:22.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  律  你…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.71,0:19:26.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,病好啦～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.84,0:19:30.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好你个头啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.50,0:19:33.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好躺着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.72,0:19:35.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还发着烧呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.34,0:19:38.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.82,0:19:42.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陪到我睡着嘛～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.32,0:19:44.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了  澪～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.71,0:19:46.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真受不了你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.86,0:19:49.21,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（dj：所以说澪乃干脆陪跟她一起睡算啦XD）
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.05,0:19:57.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.90,0:19:58.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小律  你没事儿…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.02,0:20:00.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘘
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.98,0:20:03.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚让她睡着啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.80,0:20:10.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  为什么连唯也睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.80,0:20:12.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真受不了你们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.09,0:20:18.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痊愈！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.18,0:20:21.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标学园祭  加油吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.23,0:20:23.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢——！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.91,0:20:24.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.47,0:20:28.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学园祭的讲堂使用申请书还没交上去吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.55,0:20:33.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  对不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.32,0:20:35.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到期就是到期
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.26,0:20:36.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请通融一下吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.90,0:20:38.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.85,0:20:42.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,申请书没有按时上交是因为部长感冒缺席
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.99,0:20:43.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.48,0:20:47.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然真锅同学都说到这份上的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.63,0:20:50.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就再等一天好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.50,0:20:56.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  你真是个好人！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.01,0:20:58.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澪就拜托给你啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.52,0:21:01.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有  今后也请照顾照顾我吧～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.92,0:21:02.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.92,0:21:02.84,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（R：吃什么醋！找到好老公了(1s）
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.38,0:21:07.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是觉得「Pure·Pure」比较好吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.61,0:21:08.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没门
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.52,0:21:09.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「铁拳」呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.94,0:21:10.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像演歌一样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.90,0:21:13.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…「鞋底的口香糖」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.39,0:21:14.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你今天踩到了是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.93,0:21:16.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？你怎么知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.89,0:21:19.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,  有什么好点子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.41,0:21:21.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…「充电期间」感觉如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.19,0:21:23.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…不吉利
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.54,0:21:25.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那「爆米花蜜月」？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.55,0:21:28.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说啊   你怎么光想那种甜兮兮的玩意儿
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.95,0:21:30.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「火箭铅笔」好不好？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.80,0:21:31.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你闭嘴！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.87,0:21:33.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真他娘的烦人！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.69,0:21:35.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝个茶都不消停！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.43,0:21:37.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随便起个名字不就行了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.18,0:21:38.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.22,0:21:42.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被随意起的名字打发了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.23,0:21:47.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  算了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.59,0:21:59.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总算  乐队名决定啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.75,0:21:59.39,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（放学后茶会）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.22,0:22:03.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来就只剩下拼命练习  来迎接学园祭了！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.31,0:22:08.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.57,0:23:42.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没有退烧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.94,0:23:46.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  按照这样下去的话明天大概也…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.70,0:23:48.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偏偏在这个时候得感冒 
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.45,0:23:49.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是懒散的证明呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.11,0:23:51.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你传染给人家的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.80,0:23:52.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？是我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.24,0:23:55.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.31,0:23:59.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算骗得过大家  也骗不过我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.20,0:24:09.70,title2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)}最终回　　轻 音!


